page_title: 'Use the Azure Developer CLI to deploy resources for Azure OpenAI On Your Data'
page_description: Use this article to learn how to automate resource deployment for Azure OpenAI On Your Data.
chunk_content: Connect or create an applicationAfter running the `azd` template and uploading your data, you're ready to start using Azure OpenAI on Your Data. See the quickstart article for code samples you can use to build your applications.
